### Wireless Plans Catalog

---

**Starter Talk Plan**
Price: $25 / month

A simple plan for light users. Includes unlimited talk and text within the country and **5 GB** of high-speed data each month. After the limit, speeds slow but service continues. Good for people who mostly call, text, and occasionally browse.

---

**Everyday Connect Plan**
Price: $40 / month

Includes unlimited talk, text, and **20 GB** of high-speed data. After 20 GB, speeds slow during busy network times. Video streams in standard definition. Includes hotspot sharing up to **5 GB**.

Discount: $5 off per line when you add a second line.

---

**Stream Plus Plan**
Price: $60 / month

Designed for media use. Includes unlimited talk and text and **50 GB** of priority high-speed data. Video streams in high definition. Includes **20 GB** of hotspot data for laptops or tablets.

Discounts:

* $10 off with automatic payment
* $15 off for students with verification

---

**Unlimited Max Plan**
Price: $80 / month

Unlimited talk, text, and high-speed data with **no fixed data cap**. Data may slow during heavy network congestion after **100 GB** of usage. Video streams in full HD and hotspot use is included up to **40 GB**.

Extras included:

* International texting
* 5 GB roaming data in select countries

---

**Family Share Plan**
Price: $120 / month (up to 4 lines)

Each line receives unlimited talk and text plus **40 GB** of high-speed data. Data slows after the limit during busy periods. Includes **10 GB hotspot per line**.

Discounts:

* Add a 5th line for $20
* Free upgrade to HD streaming for all lines

---

**Traveler Plan**
Price: $90 / month

Unlimited talk and text domestically plus **30 GB high-speed data** that can be used in over 40 countries. Includes **10 GB international hotspot**. Ideal for frequent travelers who want predictable billing.

---

**Flex Data Plan**
Base Price: $20 / month

Pay only for the data you use.

Data pricing:

* First 3 GB included
* Additional data: $5 per GB
* Data stops billing after **15 GB** (effectively unlimited)

Includes unlimited talk and text.

---

**Device Bundle Discount**

When purchasing a new smartphone with any plan above:

* $10 monthly credit for 12 months on plans $60 and above
* $5 monthly credit for 12 months on plans under $60

This reduces the effective monthly service cost while paying for a new device.
